Look, Braden, show them where they're going. Where are all these boats headed?

00:17:43.560 --> 00:17:52.959
Right here. Look at the boats. This is real time. This isn't the Strait of Hormuz.

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:58.808
This is America. Look, can you show them? You're blocking it. Look at all those boats coming out of there.

00:17:58.809 --> 00:18:18.927
And then I said, "Watch what we do with Panama."Remember I said the Lord said we are going to establish ourselves very strong in the Panama Canal and we will have great oil coming out of Houston, out of this area, out of the Gulf.

00:18:18.928 --> 00:18:22.696
And I said, "Watch drill, baby, drill."Look at all those boats.

00:18:22.697 --> 00:18:31.719
They're all coming here to get our oil. So let's look at what Trump says.

00:18:31.720 --> 00:18:46.171
What does President Trump say? Do you not have it? I have it. Okay, right here.

00:18:46.172 --> 00:19:03.695
Massive numbers of completely empty oil tankers, some of the largest anywhere in the world, are headed right now to the United States to load up with the best and the sweetest oil and gas anywhere in the world.

00:19:03.696 --> 00:19:12.872
We have more oil than the next two largest oil economies combined and higher quality.

00:19:12.873 --> 00:19:20.177
We are waiting for you. Quick turnaround, President Trump.

00:19:20.178 --> 00:19:31.359
Right. Look at that. What did the Lord say was coming? This right here, ladies and gentlemen.

00:19:31.360 --> 00:19:50.884
This is what He told us was coming. And I said it. I said, 'Well, they will come in here for the sweetest oil.'It's the sweetest oil. The plan is in process.

00:19:50.885 --> 00:20:03.159
I saw oil because of this go really high, and all of a sudden, everybody's buying it for a high dollar a barrel, and it stimulates the economy.

00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:17.639
America goes—people don't realize that President Trump just pulled off the largest shift in global power ever.

00:20:17.640 --> 00:20:32.239
Trump essentially burned down the competition and said America is open for business as oil tankers are coming in droves to America to fill up.

00:20:32.240 --> 00:20:36.952
I said, 'What happens?'The Lord told us the terrorists will fall.

00:20:36.953 --> 00:20:43.469
We better pray. That's the first plan. But if it doesn't work, Plan B will be the oil.

00:20:43.470 --> 00:20:49.959
And guess what happened? Exactly what the Lord said right here.

00:20:49.960 --> 00:20:58.300
But what was it the Lord told us to watch out for now? Attacks on our oil facilities.

00:20:58.301 --> 00:21:07.372
I saw Houston, I saw Louisiana, I saw our major oil refinery in Tuttle, Oklahoma.

00:21:07.373 --> 00:21:15.839
And the Lord said, 'Do you see these men in their houses? Do you see the blueprints upon their walls?

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:24.183
They have a plan to disrupt your oil facilities to retaliate for what's happening to their economy and your economy.

00:21:24.184 --> 00:21:34.050
And they are going to try to disrupt by blowing up these things with their homemade rocket launchers.'Do you all remember that last week?

00:21:34.051 --> 00:21:37.975
We prayed over this a lot. But I told you it was coming, what the Lord showed us.

00:21:37.976 --> 00:21:48.370
And I saw them casing out the facilities on boats because they couldn't get close to them and they had to use our rivers.

00:21:48.371 --> 00:22:00.919
They were pretending to be fishing and they were looking at our nuclear facilities, our nuclear plants, our electric grid, and they were looking at our water plants.

00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:22.162
And the Lord said they will try to disrupt you in the days ahead with major electric disruptions, some of which will last up to three weeks and longer in some major cities, and people will be in the hospital suffering; it will be very hot.

00:22:22.163 --> 00:22:29.359
I said it was hot outside and it was so miserable in the summer and people die of heat stroke.

00:22:29.360 --> 00:22:36.178
Does anybody remember that? I've said this over a course of time.

00:22:36.179 --> 00:22:44.399
The Lord keeps telling us and telling us. Why? Because we can stop it. Why?

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:49.734
Because I believe with all my heart God's brought up prayer generals in this end-time army.

00:22:49.735 --> 00:22:56.399
Now, the Muslim people, He loves them, but they don't serve Him and He doesn't have a covenant with them.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:23:05.159
He has a covenant with you. He has a covenant with me. And a God that will always recognize His covenant will take care of His people.

00:23:05.160 --> 00:23:14.693
Now, you want to spit in His face and say, 'Allah is king and Allah is God and we want the virgins and we're going to blow you up infidels and we're going to kill the Jews.'Guess what?

00:23:14.694 --> 00:23:26.439
God isn't on their side. God's on the side of the believing believer that understands that Jesus Christ is Lord and He dwells in our hearts richly by faith.

00:23:26.440 --> 00:23:38.113
And He will uphold His covenant with us. Now, I know I'm a covenant man, and my wife's a covenant woman. We believe in Jesus Christ that He will provide for us.

00:23:38.114 --> 00:23:45.919
He said—the Bible says—'I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.'Are you one of those?

00:23:45.920 --> 00:23:54.159
I have to ask you again, are you one of those? Do you believe that God will provide for you in the midst of the drought, in the midst of the desert?

00:23:54.160 --> 00:24:08.279
Will you be the one that He brings the raven to take care of just like He did in the Bible? I believe it. As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:24:08.280 --> 00:24:16.679
I have had a lot and I've had little, but I'm going to tell you, God has been faithful on every single side.

00:24:16.680 --> 00:24:20.889
He has been faithful every single time. So, what are we going to do?

00:24:20.890 --> 00:24:37.159
We're going to pray that the FBI, Homeland Security, our CIA, and our Secret Service will all find the people who would try to do this in America. Why? I believe we have a covenant there.

00:24:37.160 --> 00:24:56.047
If it's not for the people who are blaspheming the Lord and saying we're not for it, like some of the far-leftists, at least we have a remnant of people that know how to pray up in here and say, 'No, as for me and mine, we're serving you, Lord, and if you don't take care of them, you're going to take care of me.

00:24:56.048 --> 00:25:03.639
And the overflow of you taking care of me is going to rain down on them, too.'Do you believe it?

00:25:03.640 --> 00:25:09.912
Because God's going to take care of you. I believe it. Do you believe He's going to take care of you? You have to believe it for yourself, too.

00:25:09.913 --> 00:25:19.029
No matter what we see around us in these last days, no matter what kind of plagues, no matter what kind of storms we see, God is going to take care of me.

00:25:19.030 --> 00:25:43.639
And if the death angel could pass by the children of Israel's house whenever they were going from the Pharaoh and all that was going on with him and they put blood on their doors—I put the anointing oil upon my door just like they did, and this represents the blood of the Lamb—if the plague and the death angel passed by their house, how much more will He do it for you?

00:25:43.640 --> 00:25:49.313
We have a better covenant. We have the covenant from Jesus's blood.

00:25:49.314 --> 00:25:53.639
He took it all for us. He suffered and died for us. And guess what?

00:25:53.640 --> 00:25:57.275
I'm a joint heir with Jesus Christ now just because of what He did for me.

00:25:57.276 --> 00:26:05.559
And you are too. He's no respecter of persons. And those that call upon the name of the Lord will be saved.

00:26:05.560 --> 00:26:12.277
And I believe what a time to show that Jesus Christ is Lord in our lives even more so.

00:26:12.278 --> 00:26:18.177
And we're the salty ones. People go, 'Man, what is it about you that you're not freaked out right now?'Why?

00:26:18.178 --> 00:26:22.989
Because I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost and He dwells on the inside of me richly by faith.

00:26:22.990 --> 00:26:29.244
And I believe that as He is, so am I in this world. Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world.

00:26:29.245 --> 00:26:34.574
A thousand shall fall at my side and 10,000 at my right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me.

00:26:34.575 --> 00:26:40.479
